## About

This is my Day 1 project of the 30-Day MERN Stack Learning Journey. The portfolio website demonstrates HTML5 semantic elements, CSS3 modern layouts (Flexbox & Grid), and responsive design principles.

---

## Features

* Fully responsive for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
* Modern clean design
* Smooth animations and hover effects
* Semantic HTML5 for SEO
* CSS Grid and Flexbox layout techniques
* Sticky navigation
* Interactive elements and functional contact form (frontend validation)

---

## Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3 (Flexbox, Grid, media queries, transitions, gradients)

---

## Sections

1. Navigation Bar – Sticky header, smooth scroll, responsive menu
2. Hero Section – Introduction and call-to-action button
3. About Me – Profile image and description
4. Skills – 4 skill cards showcasing frontend, backend, database, and tools
5. Projects – Project showcase with technology stack
6. Contact – Form with name, email, message, and validation
7. Footer – Copyright and optional social links

---

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/muhammadshoaib20/Portfolio-Website.git
```

2. Navigate to project directory:

```bash
cd Portfolio-Website
```

3. Open `index.html` in your browser or use Live Server in VS Code.

